[% META title = 'Header Template Documentation' %]
[% PageVersion = 'system/header_template.tt,v 0.01 2025/09/15 shanta Exp shanta ' %]
[% debug %]
[% IF c.session.debug_mode == 1 %]
    [% PageVersion %]
    [% "Debugging HostName: " _ HostName %]
    [%# INCLUDE 'debug.tt' %]
[% END %]

<h1>Header Template Documentation</h1>

<h2>Overview</h2>

<p>The Header.tt template provides the HTML head section for all pages in the Comserv application. It includes meta tags, CSS stylesheets, JavaScript dependencies, and theme management functionality.</p>

<h2>Location</h2>

<p><strong>File:</strong> <code>Comserv/root/Header.tt</code></p>
<p><strong>Type:</strong> Template Toolkit include file</p>
<p><strong>Usage:</strong> Included in page templates via <code>[% INCLUDE 'Header.tt' %]</code></p>

<h2>Key Features</h2>

<h3>1. Meta Tags and SEO</h3>
<ul>
<li>Character encoding (UTF-8)</li>
<li>Viewport configuration for responsive design</li>
<li>SEO meta tags (keywords, description, robots)</li>
<li>Dynamic title generation based on site and page context</li>
</ul>

<h3>2. Theme System Integration</h3>
<ul>
<li>JSON-based theme system with fallback logic</li>
<li>Site-specific theme selection</li>
<li>Session-based theme preferences</li>
<li>Dynamic CSS loading based on selected theme</li>
<li>Theme class application to body element</li>
</ul>

<h3>3. CSS Architecture</h3>
<ul>
<li>Base CSS with CSS variables</li>
<li>Theme-specific stylesheets</li>
<li>Component-specific CSS (ApiCredentials, todo)</li>
<li>Icon system with SVG support</li>
<li>Menu theming integration</li>
</ul>

<h3>4. JavaScript Dependencies</h3>
<ul>
<li>jQuery 3.5.1 for AJAX functionality</li>
<li>Custom menu and sub-menu JavaScript</li>
<li>Page switching utility function</li>
</ul>

<h2>Theme Selection Logic</h2>

<p>The template implements a sophisticated theme selection system:</p>

<pre>
1. Site-specific session theme (theme_[sitename])
2. Stash theme_name
3. Session theme_name
4. Site model theme property
5. Default theme fallback
</pre>

<h2>Debug Mode Features</h2>

<p>When debug mode is enabled (<code>c.session.debug_mode == 1</code>):</p>
<ul>
<li>Displays PageVersion information</li>
<li>Shows HostName warnings if undefined</li>
<li>Logs theme selection details</li>
<li>Displays site name information</li>
<li>Shows removed CSS reference comments</li>
</ul>

<h2>Dynamic Title Generation</h2>

<p>Page titles follow the format:</p>
<pre>[% HostName _ ': ' _ ScriptDisplayName _ ': ' _ page_title %]</pre>

<p>With automatic HostName detection if not defined:</p>
<pre>[% HostName = "http://" _ c.req.uri.host %]</pre>

<h2>Site-Specific Features</h2>

<h3>CSC Site Integration</h3>
<p>Special handling for CSC site with WHMCS interface embedding:</p>
<pre>[% IF SiteName == "CSC" %]
    [% embed('CSCWHMCSInterface') %]
[% END %]</pre>

<h2>Component-Specific CSS Loading</h2>

<p>Conditional CSS loading based on template path:</p>
<ul>
<li><strong>ApiCredentials:</strong> <code>/static/css/themes/api_credentials.css</code></li>
<li><strong>Todo System:</strong> <code>/static/css/todo.css</code></li>
</ul>

<h2>Version History</h2>

<ul>
<li><strong>v0.01 (2023/08/30):</strong> Initial header template with theme system</li>
<li><strong>Current:</strong> Enhanced with JSON-based theme system and debug features</li>
</ul>

<h2>Dependencies</h2>

<h3>CSS Files</h3>
<ul>
<li><code>/static/css/base.css</code> - Base styles with CSS variables</li>
<li><code>/static/css/themes/[theme_name].css</code> - Theme-specific styles</li>
<li><code>/static/css/theme-overrides.css</code> - Theme override styles</li>
<li><code>/static/css/menu-theme.css</code> - Menu theming</li>
<li><code>/static/css/svg-icons.css</code> - SVG icon system</li>
<li><code>/static/css/icon-fix.css</code> - Icon theme color fixes</li>
</ul>

<h3>JavaScript Files</h3>
<ul>
<li><code>https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.5.1.min.js</code> - jQuery library</li>
<li><code>/static/js/sub-menu.js</code> - Sub-menu functionality</li>
<li><code>/static/js/menu.js</code> - Main menu functionality</li>
</ul>

<h2>Usage Examples</h2>

<h3>Basic Template Inclusion</h3>
<pre>
[% INCLUDE 'Header.tt' %]
&lt;body&gt;
    &lt;!-- Page content --&gt;
&lt;/body&gt;
&lt;/html&gt;
</pre>

<h3>With Custom Page Title</h3>
<pre>
[% page_title = 'Custom Page Title' %]
[% INCLUDE 'Header.tt' %]
</pre>

<h3>With Custom Keywords and Description</h3>
<pre>
[% keywords = 'custom, keywords, here' %]
[% description = 'Custom page description' %]
[% INCLUDE 'Header.tt' %]
</pre>

<h2>Troubleshooting</h2>

<h3>Theme Not Loading</h3>
<ul>
<li>Check theme_name variable in stash or session</li>
<li>Verify theme CSS file exists in <code>/static/css/themes/</code></li>
<li>Enable debug mode to see theme selection logic</li>
</ul>

<h3>Missing Styles</h3>
<ul>
<li>Ensure base.css is loading properly</li>
<li>Check theme-overrides.css for conflicts</li>
<li>Verify component-specific CSS conditions</li>
</ul>

<h3>JavaScript Errors</h3>
<ul>
<li>Check jQuery loading from CDN</li>
<li>Verify local JavaScript files exist</li>
<li>Check browser console for specific errors</li>
</ul>

